snippet.textDisplay:
Good Start but not the best. As a Chittagonian this hits me different but the prblm is in unclear pronunciation of the Chatgaya word. I am overwhelmed after listening to this but somewhere the clear pronounce of my very own language was missing. 
Tho it’s not that bad but hope in future you'll take care of this tiny things and improvise. Love you Coke studio and wishing you all a great Happy বসন্ত উৎসব
snippet.textOriginal:
Good Start but not the best. As a Chittagonian this hits me different but the prblm is in unclear pronunciation of the Chatgaya word. I am overwhelmed after listening to this but somewhere the clear pronounce of my very own language was missing. 
Tho it’s not that bad but hope in future you'll take care of this tiny things and improvise. Love you Coke studio and wishing you all a great Happy বসন্ত উৎসব
